archimate:BusinessObject.name: Supplied System
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation: The system or system element (product or service) is delivered from the supplier to the acquirer consistent with the delivery conditions of the supply agreement

properties.value: Laut INCOSE Handbuch 4.0 - übersetzt von GfSE: Ein ausgeliefertes System ist ein System oder Systemelement (Produkt oder Service) das gemäß den Lieferbedingungen des Liefervertrages vom Zulieferen an den Besteller geliefert wird.
The system or system element (product or service) is delivered from the supplier to the acquirer consistent with the delivery conditions of the supply agreement
